  08 Dec 2002; Jack Morgan <jmorgan@gentoo.org>  kdepim-3.1_rc5.ebuild :
  Added sparc keyword

  06 Dec 2002; Rodney Rees <manson@gentoo.org> : changed sparc ~sparc keywords
 
  04 Dec 2002; Olivier Reisch <doctomoe@gentoo.org> kdepim-3.1.ebuild:
  Added ppc keyword

  23 Nov 2002; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> kdepim-3.1_rc3.ebuild,
  kdepim-3.1.ebuild :

  Enforce MAKEOPTS+=-j1 - reported by DocTomoe as necessary for ppc at least.

