*kdepim-3.0.3 (19 Aug 2002)

  19 Aug 2002; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> ChangeLog  :

  New bugfix release. Enjoy!

  30 Jul 2002; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> ChangeLog  :

  Change dep on pilot-link to >=0.11.1-r1 to take advantage of a recent
  bugfix in that new revision (#5615).

